addAdministrator(address).details: add an address to the administrators list
addAdministrator(address).return: true if the address was added to the list, false if the address was already in the list

addAmbassador(address).details: add an address to the ambassadors_ list (this can be done anytime until the premine finishes)
addAmbassador(address).return: true if the address was added to the list, false if the address was already in the list

removeAdministrator(address).details: remove an address from the administrators list
removeAdministrator(address).return: true if the address was removed from the list, false if the address wasn't in the list in the first place or not called by original administrator

removeAmbassador(address).details: remove an address from the ambassadors_ list (only do this if they take too long to buy premine - they are removed automatically during premine purchase)
removeAmbassador(address).return: true if the address was removed from the list, false if the address wasn't in the list in the first place
